HEADWORD: Firecrest
<hw>Fire"crest`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A small European kinglet (<spn>Regulus ignicapillus</spn>), having
a bright red crest; -- called also <altname>fire-crested
wren</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

